Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先向大家說聲 謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好突然哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在看水星領航員的各位觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了各位給我們帶來的暖風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級感謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美好的奇蹟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙的讓人害羞的台詞 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 持續到昨天的雨終於停歇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是個非常好的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此 但因為艾莉西亞前輩有事要出去一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就臨時歇業了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 藍華有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲要上學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此這般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和亞利亞社長也決定出門去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:37.53,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 小小的秘密之地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近全是住宅區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此在做導游的時候不會到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是新威尼斯的另一副面容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時來都是不變的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨一直下到昨天才停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一定很值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了哦 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有好多好多衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這裡有更多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾著的衣服舒舒服服地在空中暢游呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼就把衣服弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那裡有水坑…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛洗完衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中郵遞員哥哥還誇我很活潑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是活潑過頭了啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡也能看到鐘樓呢 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我來到這個城市 就沒有改變過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子有點餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我們去吃那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次在附近的店裡吃到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個讓人興奮緊張的料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 是二人份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待期待 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小時候起就喜歡把這家店的粗糧餅堆得像火山一樣吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好有歷史感哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次來的時候我們試試那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是彈麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待期待 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待期待 期待期待 期待期待 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好飽哦 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肚子餓了 去吃披薩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是鬢子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的休息日 我還想跟艾莉西亞小姐偶遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不識相的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 還是揪揪她的鬢髮當作打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那邊看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡在哪裡在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟丟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大媽 給我一個番茄披薩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長 新的洋裝到貨了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿曉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的中學同窗會阿曉你去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把我們兩個的回執寄出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個披薩好像很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 謝謝的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我的披薩 在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合適哦 太好了呢 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛洛林咖啡館的裝修開始了哦 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會變得閃閃發亮的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏捷的傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神出鬼沒的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 門打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般游客不能從這邊進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去搭電梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用不用 下次再來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 跟艾莉西亞小姐問好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼哼 這次妳跑不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 馬尾男？他在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級偷偷摸摸的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這是去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒來這裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是觀光勝地 所以附近人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可思議的是 誰都不會注意到這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華和愛麗絲 說不定連艾莉西亞前輩都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣坐著的話 就沒有人會發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在一點一點地變化著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪都找不到上去的樓梯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底是怎麼上去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…是那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒上鎖 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個寺院一目了然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…屁屁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級雙料鬢髮征服！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道厲害了吧 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷襲太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於讓我抓住妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 為什麼本大爺要尾行鬢子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這絕不是在尾行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 你居然能找到這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊上樓的樓梯很不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都不會注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 對本大爺來說是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 妳到這種地方來幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這裡有一位讓我十分在意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我偶爾會偷偷來見他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幽會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不過亞利亞社長也一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直孤單一人 從這裡眺望著大海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬢子啊 妳說的他到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳他是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說那個了 曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把頭放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能跟這位用一樣的視線眺望這裡的景色了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這不變的風景之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍會有許多高興的事情 嶄新的事情 悲傷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事情堆積起了每個日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後慢慢改變著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像雲的形狀和海的顏色在變換一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生 在不為人知的漫長數百年間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直守護著這個廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然非常美好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻也有點悲傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我啊 把這裡當成了我的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}恭喜你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會告訴別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是我們的秘密基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺和鬢子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有亞利亞社長和那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 無視掉我們 你們繼續 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾二位了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是超級路人甲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥斯拉 不准誤會！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}不要告訴艾莉西亞小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我的秘密基地啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.21,0:22:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始 這裡變成了大家的秘密基地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城市在長久的不變中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺地在改變著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己一定也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:23:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面的時候 新威尼斯和燈里姐姐會有些許的變化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 莫非我也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.42,0:23:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 妳回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…超級大謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小後輩 妳眼神好認真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼謎團啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「哎呀哎呀 呵呵」的謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次 精彩的課外教學…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:01:00.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:10.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:20.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:31.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:36.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:43.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:50.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}いつまでも 手を振りたい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ここに たしかに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:02:00.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}君といた証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ずっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:14.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}この先も 続いてる道がある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:23.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}次の坂を 登ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:27.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}また会いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:01:00.32,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾記得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:10.27,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}湧上心頭的 感動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:20.36,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴著湛藍的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.72,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎風前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:31.40,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我陶醉時 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:36.26,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我們齊聲歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:43.53,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:50.31,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}無論何時 都想揮動雙手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.60,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}確實是 曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:02:00.13,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}與你同在的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.48,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永遠如 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:14.27,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我們的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:23.00,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}攀上 下一個陡坡後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:27.76,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}我們再相見吧
